room_title: Escape room "Murder Mystery" by Enigma Escape Experience in Salem
room_description: Clyde Wilson, freelance computer/IT guy,  has been murdered!  Every month he hosts a poker game that includes various clients and friends.  This time one of them killed him!  You and your forensics team have set up a tent outside the crime scene with the purpose of reconstructing this crime.   Solve the mystery and put his widow's mind to rest.
